Hello!
This folder contain my schematic design. I made it from Ki-Cad.
In this project, I chose to not convert it to PCB so that I can just make a flexible wiring inside of the dasai mochi (wire can bend while PCB not).
Not only that this would save up some cost, as PCB printing here (in Indonesia) cost around IDR 100.000 or around USD 6 (Just for one PCB).
This schematic can be the guide for you to connect the components, just follow the wire connect what pin to what pin.. It should be fine
